globalblocking-block:
{{doc-special|GlobalBlock}}

This title is used when global blocks on accounts are disabled.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-block-new}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-unblock}}

{{Identical|Globally block IP address}}

globalblocking-block-intro:
{{Doc-specialpagesummary|globalblock}}Used as an introductory text on Special:GlobalBlock form.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-modify-intro}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-block-intro-new}}

globalblocking-block-edit-dropdown:
Shown beneath the global block form on the right side. It is a link to {{msg-mw|globalblocking-block-reason-dropdown|notext=1}}.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|ipb-edit-dropdown}}

globalblocking-block-legend:
Used as legend for the fieldset around the input form of Special:GlobalBlock.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-block-legend-new}}

globalblocking-block-submit:
Used as submit button text on Special:GlobalBlock form.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-modify-submit}}
* {{msg-mw|ipbsubmit}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-block-submit-new}}

globalblocking-modify-submit:
Used as submit button text on Special:GlobalBlock form when modifying an existing global block.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-block-submit}}
* {{msg-mw|ipb-change-block}}

globalblocking-block-success:
Used in [[Special:GlobalBlock]]. Parameters:
* $1 - IP address

See also: {{msg-mw|globalblocking-modify-success}}

globalblocking-modify-success:
Used in [[Special:GlobalBlock]] as a success message indicating that a global block was successfully modified. Parameters:
* $1 - IP address, IP range, or username

See also: {{msg-mw|globalblocking-block-success}}

globalblocking-local-failed:
Shown if blocking an IP address locally failed.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-local-failed-new}}

globalblocking-also-local:
Form label for a checkbox asking to also block the IP on the local wiki.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-also-local-new}}

globalblocking-search-legend:
Used as legend of the fieldset around the input form of Special:GlobalBlockList

See also:
* {{msg-mw|ipblocklist-legend}}
 *{{msg-mw|globalblocking-block-legend}}

globalblocking-search-submit:
Used as submit button text on Special:GlobalBlockList form.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|Ipblocklist-submit}}

globalblocking-list-tempblocks:
Used as the label for the multi-select checkbox in the form on [[Special:GlobalBlockList]]. When checked, this hides blocks which have non-indefinite expiry.

See also:
*{{msg-mw|blocklist-tempblocks}}

globalblocking-list-indefblocks:
Used as the label for the multi-select checkbox in the form on [[Special:GlobalBlockList]]. When checked, this hides all blocks with an indefinite expiry.

See also:
*{{msg-mw|blocklist-indefblocks}}

globalblocking-list-addressblocks:
Used as the label for the multi-select checkbox in the form on [[Special:GlobalBlockList]]. When checked, this hides all blocks where the target is a single IP address.

See also:
*{{msg-mw|blocklist-addressblocks}}

globalblocking-list-rangeblocks:
Used as the label for the multi-select checkbox in the form on [[Special:GlobalBlockList]]. When checked, this hides all blocks where the target is a IP address range.

See also:
*{{msg-mw|blocklist-rangeblocks}}

globalblocking-infiniteblock:
Part of the log entry of user block in [[Special:GlobalBlockList]]. Shown if the block has an indefinite expiry.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-expiringblock}}

Can be identical to {{msg-mw|infiniteblock}}

{{Identical|Infinite}}

globalblocking-list-noresults:
Shown on Special:GlobalBlockList when no global blocks are found. This can occur when the target is invalid or if there are no global blocks on the target.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|ipblocklist-no-results}}

globalblocking-goto-block:
Navigation link to Special:GlobalBlock.
{{Identical|Globally block IP address}}

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-goto-status}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-goto-unblock}}

globalblocking-goto-unblock:
Navigation link to Special:GlobalUnblock. Shown below the title of Special:GlobalBlock, Special:GlobalBlockList and Special:GlobalBlockStatus.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-goto-block}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-goto-status}}

globalblocking-goto-status:
Navigation link to Special:GlobalBlockWhitelist. Shown below the title of Special:GlobalBlock, Special:GlobalBlockList and Special:GlobalBlockWhitelist.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-goto-block}}
* {{msg-mw|globalblocking-goto-unblock}}

globalblocking-return:
Link to Special:GlobalBlockList. Shown on Special:GlobalWhiteList and Special:GlobalUnblock below the success message.

Success messages:
*{{msg-mw|globalblocking-block-success}}
*{{msg-mw|globalblocking-modify-success}}
*{{msg-mw|globalblocking-unblock-unblocked}}
*{{msg-mw|globalblocking-whitelist-whitelisted}}
*{{msg-mw|globalblocking-whitelist-dewhitelisted}}

globalblocking-unblock-legend:
