globalblocking-logentry-expiry:
Used as a flag. Parameters:
* $1 - expiry time and date
{{Identical|Expire}}

globalblocking-logentry-noexpiry:
Used as a flag on global block log when the expiry is not set.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|expiry}}

