Used as link title in [[Special:Contributions]] and in [[Special:DeletedContributions]].

See also:
* {{msg-mw|change-blocklink}}

globalblocking-contribs-remove:
Used as link title in [[Special:Contributions]] and in [[Special:DeletedContributions]].

